    <entry>
      <title>7.1运算符</title>
      <link href="/2023/03/14/7-1%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6/"/>
      <url>/2023/03/14/7-1%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>i++与++i的区别</p><p>一，在c语言的内建型别：</p><p>i++；</p><p>++i；</p><p>在c++里，i是一个对象，++i的效率比i++的效率高</p><p>二、在复合表达式或赋值语句里：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">int i=0；</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">int a=i++；// a=i；i=i+1；--&gt;a==0,i==1</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">int i=0;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">int b=++i; // i=i+1;b=i; --&gt;b==1,i==1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>三，在函数中：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">int i =0;</span><br><span class="line">printf(&quot;i:%d\n&quot;,i++); //输出0</span><br><span class="line">i=0;</span><br><span class="line">printf(&quot;i:%d\n&quot;,++i); //输出1</span><br><span class="line">i=0;</span><br><span class="line">printf(&quot;%d %d\n&quot;,i++,++i); //输出取决于编译器</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>6.1输入输出</title>
      <link href="/2023/03/13/6-1%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA/"/>
      <url>/2023/03/13/6-1%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1.输入一个变量需要&amp;符号，而输入字符串不需要</p><p>2.%S或%ws输入宽字节</p><p>3.scanf_s比scanf更为安全，scanf可能产生缓冲区溢出漏洞。</p><p>4.scanf输入字符串遇到空格就结束，gets可以将空格包含进去。</p><p>5.gets_s比gets更为安全。</p><p>6.getch输入字符不会回显在屏幕上，也不需要按回车键。getchar输入字符会回显在屏幕上，需要按回车键。</p><p>7._getch比getch更为安全。</p><p>8.4996警告说明存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
